---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CallToAction from '../../components/CallToAction.astro';
---

<Layout title="Understanding the Benefits of One-to-One Care - St Catherine's Group Blog" description="Discover why personalized, one-to-one care can make all the difference in maintaining independence, dignity, and quality of life.">
    <Navbar />

    <!-- Article Header -->
    <article class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <!-- Breadcrumb -->
            <nav class="mb-8">
                <a href="/blog" class="text-green-dark hover:underline">← Back to Blog</a>
            </nav>

            <!-- Meta Info -->
            <div class="mb-6">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-dark/10 text-green-dark text-xs font-medium rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Care Insights
                </span>
            </div>

            <!-- Title -->
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
                Understanding the Benefits of One-to-One Care
            </h1>

            <!-- Article Meta -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-gray-600 mb-12 pb-8 border-b border-gray-200">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>14th March 2024</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>5 min read</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Featured Image -->
            <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-200 rounded-2xl mb-12">
                <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-green-dark/20 to-green-dark/40 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl">
                    <span class="text-white text-lg font-medium">Featured Article Image</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Article Content -->
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-gray-800 font-light mb-8">
                    In a world where healthcare often feels rushed and impersonal, one-to-one care stands apart as a beacon of what compassionate support should truly be.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">What is One-to-One Care?</h2>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    One-to-one care means exactly what it says: dedicated, personalized support where one care professional focuses entirely on one individual. Unlike shared care models where attention is divided among multiple people, one-to-one care ensures you receive undivided attention, tailored support, and the time needed to address your unique needs and preferences.
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    This approach transforms healthcare from a standardized service into a truly personal experience, where the care you receive is as individual as you are.
                </p>

                <div class="my-12 pl-8 border-l-4 border-green-dark bg-warm-50 p-6 rounded-r-xl">
                    <p class="text-2xl font-light italic text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
                        "The difference isn't just in the care itself—it's in the relationship, the understanding, and the genuine human connection that comes from dedicated attention."
                    </p>
                </div>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">The Key Benefits</h2>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Personalized Attention</h3>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    With one-to-one care, everything is tailored to you. Your care professional gets to know your routines, preferences, personality, and needs intimately. They understand that you prefer your tea with milk first, that you find mornings easier than afternoons, and that you need a moment of quiet before engaging in activities.
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    This level of personalization simply isn't possible when care is shared among multiple individuals. Your needs don't have to compete for attention—they receive it fully.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Building Meaningful Relationships</h3>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    When the same care professional works with you consistently, something profound happens: a real relationship develops. This isn't just about familiarity—it's about trust, understanding, and genuine companionship.
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    These relationships become a source of comfort, stability, and joy. You're not just receiving care from a stranger each day; you're spending time with someone who knows you, cares about you, and genuinely wants to see you thrive.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Better Health Outcomes</h3>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    Research consistently shows that personalized, consistent care leads to better health outcomes. When your care professional knows you well, they notice subtle changes in your wellbeing that might otherwise go undetected. A slight change in mood, energy levels, or appetite becomes significant when observed by someone who knows your normal patterns.
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    This early detection can prevent small issues from becoming serious problems, ensuring interventions happen at the right time.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Enhanced Dignity and Independence</h3>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    One-to-one care respects your dignity in ways that shared care models often struggle to achieve. With dedicated attention, you can maintain your routines, make choices about how you spend your time, and receive support in a way that feels natural and respectful rather than institutional.
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    Independence isn't about doing everything alone—it's about having the right support to live life on your terms. One-to-one care provides that support without diminishing autonomy.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Who Benefits Most?</h2>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    While one-to-one care benefits everyone, it's particularly valuable for:
                </p>

                <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
                        <span class="text-green-dark mt-1">•</span>
                        <span>Individuals with complex health needs requiring specialized attention</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
                        <span class="text-green-dark mt-1">•</span>
                        <span>People living with dementia who benefit from familiar faces and routines</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
                        <span class="text-green-dark mt-1">•</span>
                        <span>Those at risk of falls or requiring safety monitoring</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
                        <span class="text-green-dark mt-1">•</span>
                        <span>Anyone experiencing loneliness or social isolation</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
                        <span class="text-green-dark mt-1">•</span>
                        <span>Individuals who simply value personalized, attentive care</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">The St Catherine's Group Approach</h2>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    At St Catherine's Group, one-to-one care isn't just a service we offer—it's the foundation of everything we do. We believe that exceptional care begins with dedicated attention, genuine relationships, and a deep commitment to seeing each person as the unique individual they are.
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    Our team members are carefully selected not just for their qualifications and experience, but for their compassion, patience, and ability to build meaningful connections. We provide ongoing training, support, and supervision to ensure they can deliver the highest quality one-to-one care.
                </p>

                <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
                        If you're considering care for yourself or a loved one, we'd welcome the opportunity to discuss how our one-to-one approach might benefit you. Every person deserves care that honors their individuality, respects their dignity, and supports them to live their best possible life.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Share & Back -->
            <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 flex items-center justify-between">
                <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-green-dark font-semibold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
                    </svg>
                    Back to Blog
                </a>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Share this article:</span>
                    <div class="flex gap-3">
                        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-dark/10 hover:bg-green-dark text-green-dark hover:text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-colors" aria-label="Share on Twitter">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path d="M23 3a10.9 10.9 0 01-3.14 1.53 4.48 4.48 0 00-7.86 3v1A10.66 10.66 0 013 4s-4 9 5 13a11.64 11.64 0 01-7 2c9 5 20 0 20-11.5a4.5 4.5 0 00-.08-.83A7.72 7.72 0 0023 3z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-dark/10 hover:bg-green-dark text-green-dark hover:text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-colors" aria-label="Share on Facebook">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 00-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 011-1h3z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-dark/10 hover:bg-green-dark text-green-dark hover:text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-colors" aria-label="Share on LinkedIn">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 016 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 00-2-2 2 2 0 00-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 016-6zM2 9h4v12H2z"></path>
                                <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>

    <CallToAction />
    <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Enhanced typography for blog content */
    .prose h2 {
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
    }

    .prose h3 {
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
    }
</style>
